### [Psalms Chapter 81](../../../bib/kjv/psa081.htm#001.md)

[Psalms](../../../bib/kjv/psa001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">psa 81:0</span></span>

Overview

[Psa 81:1](../../../bib/kjv/psa081.htm#001.md), An exhortation to a solemn
praising of God; [Psa 81:4](../../../bib/kjv/psa081.htm#004.md), God
challenges that duty by reason of his benefits; [Psa
81:8](../../../bib/kjv/psa081.htm#008.md), God, exhorting to obedience,
complains of their disobedience, which proves their own hurt.

